    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <pb facs="12180628" />
                <head type="title"><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>St Goar</head><!-- DCH: Check when we have image.-->
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We passed a rock, whose bare front ever</l>
                    <l>Had borne the brunt of wind and weather<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">405</add></l>
                    <l>And downwards by the <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> we bore</l>
                    <l>Upon the village of <placeName corresp="#STGOAR">St Goar</placeName></l>
                    <l>That mid the hills embosomed <del>th</del> lay</l>
                    <l>Where the <geogName corresp="#RHINE">Rhine</geogName> checked his onward way</l>
                    <l>And lay the mighty crags between<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">410</add></l>
                    <l>As if enamoured of the scene</l>
                    <l>It loved not on its way to wind</l>
                    <l>And leave a spot so fair behind</l>
                    <l>For grim the <subst><del rend="strikethrough">passage</del><add>chasm</add></subst> through whose cleft</l>
                    <l>The waters had a passage reft<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">415</add></l>
                    <l>And gaunt the gorge that yawned before</l>
                    <l>Through which a passage <add place="above"><space quantity="15" unit="chars"/>emerging</add> they must roar</l>
                    <l>No marvel they should love to rest</l>
                    <l>And peaceful spread their placid breast</l>
                    <l>Before in fury driving dread<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">420</add></l>
                    <l>Tormented on his rocky bed</l>
                    <l>Or flinging far his scattering spray</l>
                    <l>Oer the peaked rocks that bar his way</l>
                    <l>Wave upon wave at random tost</l>
                    <l>Or in the giddy whirlpool lost<add rend="linenumber-right-JR">425</add></l>
                    <l>And now are undisturbed sleeping</l>
                    <l>No more on rocks his billows beating</l>
                    <l>But lightly laughing laps the tide</l>
                    <l>Where stoop the vineyards to his side</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
